Hello <%= @user.full_name %>,
<br /><br />
Thank you for adding your restaurant to forkfile.com! We have created a Forkfile account for you that has web
access enabled for <%= @restaurant.name %>. This means that you can access your orders online from our website.
<br /><br />
The first thing you need to do is click on this link and set your password:
<br /><br />
<%= @url %>
<br /><br />
Once you do that, you are all set to view your orders! To access your orders from the forkfile.com website, login using 
your email and password, and then click on "My Profile" at the top right of any page. There is a section called 
"You are the owner of the following restaurants". <%= @restaurant.name %> will be listed here. When you click on the 
restaurant link, you will be navigated to your orders page. Select an order to see more information.
<br /><br />
As always, please contact us if you have any questions.
